milquetoast doesnt square with the popular and savvy gop 
politician she has come to know on capitol hill 
at the annual house gym parties where bush shows up to have his 
picture taken with democrats and republicans alike hes one of 
the boys said oakar 
frankly on a onetoone basis he is not the socalled 
elitist type that he appears to be he is much more appealing 
in a smaller crowd than he is on dan rathers show she said 
i think george bush is much more formidable than a lot of 
