the family of a 56yearold comatose woman 
can order doctors to remove the feeding tube keeping her alive and 
grant what relatives say would have been her wish to die a judge 
ruled monday 
carol mcconnell a registered nurse who suffered permanent brain 
damage in a car accident three years ago remains in a coma at a 
