<TEXT>
room 890 in the intensive care unit of the 
banacha street hospital is spacious and clean its neurological 
unit has four new heartmonitors and stateoftheart respirators 
but it has not had a patient in the last two years 
we have equipment worth tens of thousands of dollars but we 
