to support themselves in other ways she says 
her days are long these days 9 to 5 in the office most nights 
in rehearsal no time for social life a recent romance fizzled 
blame her busy schedule 
right now im involved with the bel canto opera which is a 
small opera company she says im doing the part of a satyr 
which is half human male half goat its my second male part in a 
year i dont know what theyre trying to tell me they told me 
its definitely not typecasting 
