clothes 
recently an executive in her company relayed word that she 
should dress more appropriately in her office forgo the stretch 
pants that she was wont to wear 
they were formfitting she says laughing this day i was 
dressed for the theater i thought i looked rather nice i had on a 
nice black top and black highheel shoes a day or two later i was 
told i have to learn to project a corporate image 
trudy says re koster an elderly but wellknown voice teacher in 
