issuing approximately 50 million shares of new stock in mgm to be 
sold for 8 a share 
barris industries will buy 25 percent of the new stock for 100 
million 
present holders of mgmua will get rights to buy the rest and 
kerkorian has agreed to exercise all his rights giving him at 
least 57 percent of the new mgm kerkorian also will buy any shares 
that arent bought by mgmua public shareholders the companies 
said 
under the arrangement mgmua will sell 50 million shares of new 
stock in mgm for 8 a share 
of the proceeds 100 million would come back to mgm and 300 
million will be used in part to pay off its 230 million bank debt 
